# Insights

Non-obvious patterns. Strategic truths. Wildcards. Things worth re-reading in a year.

> **What goes here:** lenses, not action items. Insights that, if you forgot them, would cost you something subtle but important. The exocortex adds to this file whenever something genuinely non-obvious surfaces during briefings or conversations. You should add to it too — whenever you have one of those "huh, that's interesting" moments, write it down.

> **What does NOT go here:** todos, reminders, things you might do this week. Those go in `commitments.md` or `life.md`. Insights are the *meta* layer.

> **3-year test:** if you wouldn't still find this useful in 3 years, don't put it here.

---

